      <text>PT.5.9 (Ratio of sum of cosines and sines)</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>
Express \(\dfrac{\cos({@b1@}x)-\cos({@a1@}x)}{\sin({@b1@}x)+\sin({@a1@}x)}\) as \(\tan(nx)\) for an integer \(n\).
<p></p><p>\( \dfrac{\cos({@b1@}x)-\cos({@a1@}x)}{\sin({@b1@}x)+\sin({@a1@}x)}=\) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="html">
      <text>\(\cos({@b1@}x)-\cos({@a1@}x)\equiv 2 \sin({@A1@}x)\sin({@B1@}x)\qquad
\sin({@b1@}x)+\sin({@a1@}x)\equiv 2\sin({@A1@}x)\cos(-{@B1@}x)\)
\(\qquad\therefore\qquad \dfrac{\cos({@b1@}x)-\cos({@a1@}x)}{\sin({@b1@}x)+\sin({@a1@}x)}\equiv \dfrac{\sin({@B1@}x)}{\cos(-{@B1@}x)}\equiv 
\dfrac{\sin({@B1@}x)}{\cos({@B1@}x)}\equiv \tan({@B1@}x)\)</text>
    </generalfeedback>
